Florence Lake https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Florence_Lake 0 Florence Lake (born Florence Silverlake, November 27, 1904 – April 11, 1980) was an American actress best known as the leading lady in most of the Edgar Kennedy comedy shorts.
